<br />Pretty neat if you had a famicom, all you had to do to get an extra credit would be to blow into the microphone. 
<br />
<br />I assume the Japanese cartridge port of Legend of Zelda does not use the microphone because it was ported from the U.S. cartridge and the text translated back into Japanese.  It was also released in 1994, probably when the Famicom AV was the only choice on the market, which did not support the microphone.

		

